         <div type="commentary">
            <head>Commentary</head>
            <p>See Aurigemma for individual inscriptions.</p>
            <p>
               Of the 121 tombs located and examined, 59 yielded
            some part of the inscriptions with which each was originally covered.</p>
            <p>
               The whole complex has been ascribed by
               Aurigemma to the period of Vandal domination preceding the Byzantine reconquest of
               531.</p>
